  <summary date="2021-04-22T16:24:19Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Universal Giving Pandemic Response and Recovery Act

This bill allows individual taxpayers who do not otherwise itemize their tax deductions a deduction in taxable years beginning in 2021 or 2022 for charitable contributions. The deduction is limited to one-third of the standard deduction allowed to such taxpayers.</summary>
